{"tid":577150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西九龍高鐵站上蓋估值達790億至950億元 完全抵銷起高鐵開支","createTime":"2018-03-01T13:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T03:57:08.000Z","uid":10540,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"5a22b7a7e5467dd5df42bd3b454bdeec012406cd","tid":577150,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2020000/2020374/HKET_20180301_A03_01AC003_P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2020000%2F2020374%2FHKET_20180301_A03_01AC003_P.jpg&h=450be17e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本年度批出7幅工商業地，帶來611億元賣地收益，佔全年賣地收入超過一半，當中先後誕生中環美利道及啟德兩幅百億商業地王。政府指下年度將推4幅商業/酒店用地，樓面面積約570萬平方呎，將較17/18年度的185萬平方呎多2倍。估計不乏樓面逾百萬平方呎的大型市區商業地。<br />\n<br />\n廣深港高鐵香港段將於今年通車，預期上蓋商業項目有機會納入賣地計劃，初步計劃寫字樓樓面約285萬平方呎，另設31萬平方呎零售商場，總樓面約316萬平方呎，媲美環球貿易廣場（ICC），綜合市場估值達790億至950億元；寫字樓樓面呎價約2.5萬至3萬元，估計將分期推出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.hket.com/article/2020374/4%E5%95%86%E5%9C%B0%E7%B4%8D%E8%B3%A3%E5%9C%B0%20%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E4%B8%8A%E8%93%8B%E6%96%99%E6%88%90%E5%9C%B0%E7%8E%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2020374%2F4%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25B4%258D%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E5%259C%25B0%2520%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2590%25B5%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%2593%258B%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%258E%258B&d=iDxFWRhawt42ovs5%2Fyu4VG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2517d471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.hket.com/article/2020374/4%E5%95%86%E5%9C%B0%E7%B4%8D%E8%B3%A3%E5%9C%B0%20%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E4%B8%8A%E8%93%8B%E6%96%99%E6%88%90%E5%9C%B0%E7%8E%8B</a>"},{"pid":"c37e605100ada4463f7cd8515e95ce3f92aa31fa","tid":577150,"uid":53794,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:18:50.000Z","msg":"將所有野變成樓就得 港畜會自動奉上一切"},{"pid":"8e94601848325fdb39d5e5f082094e28852ec4c7","tid":577150,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0